snippet: The approval of the cabinet brings to an end months of uncertainty about who was in charge of the government.
abstract: Libyan Parliament votes overwhelmingly to approve cabinet proposed by Prime Min Ali Zeidan, ending months of uncertainty about who is in charge of government.

byline.contributor: Suliman Ali Zway contributed reporting from Tripoli, Libya.
